#: includes/eme-formfields.php:311
msgid "Field type"
msgstr "字段类型"

#: includes/eme-formfields.php:313
msgid "For the types 'Date (JS)','Datetime (JS)' and 'Time (JS)' you can optionally enter a custom date format in 'HTML Field attributes' to be used when the field is shown."
msgstr "对于 \"日期（JS）\"、\"日期时间（JS）\" 和 \"时间（JS）\" 的类型，您可以选择在 \"HTML 字段属性\" 中输入一个自定义的日期格式，在字段显示时使用。"

#: includes/eme-formfields.php:315
msgid "For the type 'File' you can optionally enter a maximum upload size in MB in 'Field values'."
msgstr "对于 \"文件\" 类型，您可以选择在 \"字段值\" 中输入最大上传尺寸（MB）。"

#: includes/eme-formfields.php:319
msgid "Field purpose"
msgstr "字段目的"

#: includes/eme-formfields.php:331
msgid "If you select 'RSVP field', 'People field' or 'Members field', this field will show up as an extra column in the overview table for bookings, people or members. Selecting 'Generic' will cause it to show up in the overview table for bookings or members."
msgstr "如果您选择 \"RSVP字段\"、\"人们字段 \" 或 \"会员字段\"，这个字段将作为一个额外的列显示在预订、人们或会员的总表中。选择 “通用” 将导致它显示在预订或会员的总表中。"

#: includes/eme-formfields.php:332
msgid "If you select 'People field' you can add a condition to this field, meaning that if the person is in the group you selected in the condition, this is an extra field that will then be available to fill out for that person. This allows you to put people in e.g. a Volunteer group and then ask for more volunteer info."
msgstr "如果您选择了 \"人员字段\"，您可以给这个字段添加一个条件，也就是说，如果这个人在您在条件中选择的群组中，这就是一个额外的字段，然后可以为这个人填写。这允许您把人放在例如一个志愿者组中，然后询问更多的志愿者信息。"

#: includes/eme-formfields.php:333
msgid "If you select 'People field' and use this field in a RSVP or membership form, the info will be stored to the person, so you can ask for extra personal info when someone signs up. When editing the person, those fields will then be visible."
msgstr "如果您选择了 \"人员字段\"，并在 RSVP 或会员表格中使用这个字段，信息将被存储到这个人身上，所以您可以在有人注册时要求提供额外的个人信息。当编辑这个人时，这些字段将是可见的。"

#: includes/eme-formfields.php:334
msgid "If you select 'Events field', 'Locations field' or 'Memberships field', this field will be used in the definition of the event, location or membership. Warning: this is unrelated to the use of custom fields in RSVP forms, so if you don't intend to use this field in the definition of events, locations or memberships, don't select this."
msgstr "如果您选择 \"活动字段\"、\"地点字段 \"或 \"会籍字段\"，这个字段将被用于活动、地点或会籍的定义中。警告：这与 RSVP 表格中的自定义字段的使用无关，所以如果您不打算在活动、地点或会籍的定义中使用这个字段，就不要选择这个。"

#: includes/eme-formfields.php:345
msgid "Include in CSV export"
msgstr "包括在 CSV 导出中"

#: includes/eme-formfields.php:347
msgid "Include this field in the CSV export for bookings."
msgstr "在 CSV 导出的预订中包括这个字段。"

#: includes/eme-formfields.php:351
#: includes/eme-formfields.php:3412
msgid "Field condition"
msgstr "字段条件"

#: includes/eme-formfields.php:353
msgid "Only show this field if the person is member of the selected group. Leave empty to add this field to all people."
msgstr "只有当这个人是所选群组的会员时才显示这个字段。留空则将此字段添加到所有的人。"

#: includes/eme-formfields.php:357
#: includes/eme-options.php:78
msgid "Required field"
msgstr "必须填写"

#: includes/eme-formfields.php:359
msgid "Use this if the field is required to be filled out."
msgstr "如果该字段是必须填写的，则使用此选项。"

#: includes/eme-formfields.php:360
msgid "This overrides the use of \"#REQ\" when defining a field in a form."
msgstr "当在表格中定义一个字段时，这取代了 \"#REQ\" 的使用。"

#: includes/eme-formfields.php:363
msgid "Searchable or sortable"
msgstr "可搜索或可排序"

#: includes/eme-formfields.php:365
msgid "When defining a custom field, it is also used in the administration interface for events, locations, people, members (depending on its purpose)."
msgstr "当定义一个自定义字段时，它也会在管理界面上用于事件、地点、人员、会员（取决于其目的）。"

#: includes/eme-formfields.php:366
msgid "However, being able to search or sort on such a field is more heavy on the database, that is why by default this parameter is set to \"No\"."
msgstr "然而，能够在这样一个字段上进行搜索或排序对数据库来说是比较沉重的，这就是为什么默认情况下这个参数被设置为 \"否\"。"

#: includes/eme-formfields.php:367
msgid "If you want to search or sort on such a field, set this parameter to \"Yes\"."
msgstr "如果您想对这样的字段进行搜索或排序，请将此参数设置为 \"是\"。"

#: includes/eme-formfields.php:372
msgid "Use this if the field indicates an extra charge to the total price (can be negative to indicate a discount), in which case you should also set the field value to the charge."
msgstr "如果该字段表示对总价的额外收费（可以为负数表示折扣），请使用此选项，在这种情况下您还应将字段值设置为收费金额。"

#: includes/eme-formfields.php:373
#, fuzzy
msgid "For multivalue fields (like e.g. dropdown) the field values should indicate the price for that selection (and the price needs to be unique)."
msgstr "这只对多值字段（如下拉式）真正有用，在这种情况下，字段值应表明该选择的价格（而且价格需要是唯一的）。"

#: includes/eme-formfields.php:374
msgid "This is ignored for fields with purpose 'Events field', 'Locations field' or 'Memberships field'"
msgstr "对于具有 \"活动字段\"、\"地点字段 \"或 \"会籍字段\" 目的的字段将被忽视。"

